snippet.textDisplay: For those who don't understand kashmiri, this song is a satire on the recent tradition of holding extravagant weddings as a showoff of one's social status which has made it very difficult for poor n lower middle class families in marrying off their daughters. As a result of this custom, Kashmir has highest number of unmarried youth in India, ages between 18-30. which is 29%
